    "feat": {
        "name": "Mask of The 15th Step",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You have ascended to the 15th Step and stand among the greatest of Razmir\u2019s priests. You can Craft your Razmiri mask out of gold or upgrade your existing mask to a gold one in the same time it takes to Craft one made of iron. A gold Razmiri mask grants a +3 item bonus to Deception checks to Lie or Feint, is a 14th-level item, and gains the following activation in addition to those possessed by the standard and silver masks.   \n  \n**Activate\u2014Call Upon Razmir\u2019s Wrath** (concentrate, manipulate, occult)",
        "level": 14,
        "traits": [
            {
